description: With eight family restaurants, three themed gourmet trucks, a full service studio and special events catering company spanning the globe, serving people great food is our lifetime passion. My husband and I have been lucky to have lived and traveled in many countries throughout our years, and have been inspired to bring the beautiful bits of culture and authentic flavors from around the world to our eateries here at home.Hang 10 Tacos is your classic taco truck infused with California love. We bring you the traditional tacos and burritos created for the for the appetite of the true Californian. Each taco was created to represent a different beach on the California coast. Our tacos are made with the freshest and finest ingredients with robust flavors. Our sauces are handmade and are sure to satisfy the toughest critics. We bring you the taste of street tacos with upscale quality.
name: Hang 10 Tacos
